snippet.textDisplay:
Emperor: I have been every voice.
Snoke: you have ever heard.
Vader: inside your head.

Emperor: I’m no puppeteer Ben. I don’t make things happen. It doesn’t work like that.

Ben: what did you do to me?

Emperor: free will. It’s like butterfly wings. Once touched they never get off the ground. I only set the stage. You pull your own strings.

Ben: what did you do to me?

Emperor: a lightsaber? In here?

Ben: DAMM IT!!! WHAT DID YOU DO TO ME?!!!!

Emperor: well... on a scale of 1-10... 10 being the most evil act of destroying the Jedi order and 1 being your average slaughtering a village of sand people. I’d say, not to be cruel... you and I got it on about a 7.

Ben: FUCK YOU!!!! (Slashes the emperor)

Emperor: Got me!!!! Got me!!!! Yes!!!!! Step it up son!!!! Come on!!!!! That’s good!!!! You got to hold on to the fury! That’s the last thing to go! That’s the final hiding place. It’s the final fig leaf.

Ben: who are you?

Emperor: who am I? Who are you? Supreme leader of the first order. Leader of the knights of Ren. Why? Why do you think? Because you’re so fucking good. Yes. But why?

Ben: because you’re my grandfathers creator?

Emperor: I’m a little more than that Ben, awfully hot in that throne room, wasn’t it? What’s the mission, Ben? To finish what you started, Ben. Time to let old things die.

Ben: what are you?

Emperor: I have so many names.

Ben: sidious?

Emperor: call me great grandfather.

Ben: skywalker, luke, he knew it. He knew it. He knew it, so you destroyed him and the Jedi order.

Emperor: you’re blaming me for skywalker? I hope you’re kidding. Luke you could have saved him and the Jedi order anytime you wanted. All he wanted was a good student. You wanted power.

Ben: that’s a lie.

Emperor: face it you wanted to be powerful ever since you learned your heritage.

Ben: that’s not true. You don’t know what we had.

Emperor: I’m on your side.

Ben: you’re a liar! (Goes to leave)

Emperor: there’s nothing out there for you. Don’t be a paln of the Jedi. Stop deluding yourself. Skywalker told you to control your feelings. What did he say? “Reach out with your feelings” didn’t he say that? What did you do? “I will destroy you, and her, and all of it” remember?

Ben: I know what you did. You set me up!

Emperor: who told you to become this evil great creation? Who made that choice?

Ben: it’s entrapment. You set me up!

Emperor: and Han? The direction you took! Hutts, slavers, federation, all feeding at the same trough. Who’s ideas were those?

Ben: you played me!

Emperor: it was a test! Your test! And Rey, knowing she could possibly turn. Seeing her power! What did you do? You offered to train her!

Ben: you brought me in. You put me there! You made her powerful!

Emperor: I don’t do that, Ben! The day you spoke to the helmet what did I say to you? What were my words to you? The call to the light, you didn’t want it.

Ben: Light!!!!! I don’t follow the light!!!! I’m powerful!!!! I’m powerful!!!!! I’m a supreme leader!!!!! That’s my job that’s what I do!!!!!

Emperor: I rest my case. Skywalker Blood... definitely my favorite influence. Ben it’s so basic. Self-love. The unlimited power. It’s not that you didn’t care for skywalker, Ben... it’s just that you were a little more involved with someone else. Yourself.

Ben: you’re right. I did it all. I betrayed him. I let the light side go.

Emperor: don’t be too hard on yourself, Ben. You wanted something more. Believe me. I left plagius behind and just kept going. You can’t keep punishing yourself. It’s awesome how far you’ve come. I didn’t make it easy. Couldn’t. Not for you. I’ve had so many apprentices. I’ve had so many disappointments. Mistake after mistake. Then there’s you.

Ben: what do you want from me?

Emperor: I want you to be yourself. You know, I tell you boy... guilt... it’s like a bag of fucking bricks. All you got to do... is set it down. Ik what you’re going through. I’ve been there. Let it go.

Ben: I can’t do that.

Emperor: who you carrying all those bricks for? Skywalker? I tell you... let me give you a little inside information about Skywalker. Skywalker likes to watch. He’s a prankster. Think about it. He gives man... instincts. He gives you these extraordinary gift, and then what does he do? I swear for his own amusement... his own private, cosmic... gag reel... he sets the rules in opposition. It’s the goof of all time. Feel, but don’t think. Reach out, but don’t take. And while you’re jumping from one foot to the other what is he doing? He’s laughing his sick fucking ass off! He’s a tightass! He’s a failure! He’s a supposed keeper of the peace! Follow that? Never!

Ben: better to reign in the dark then serve the light. Is that it?

Emperor: why not? I’m here on the ground with my nose in it since the whole thing began. I’ve nurtured every power a sith desires to have. I cared about what skywalker wanted and I never judged him. Why? Because I never rejected him, inspite all of his imperfections. I’m a fan. I’m a Sith Lord. Maybe the last Sith Lord. Who, in their right mind... Ben, could possibly deny... the galaxy was entirely mine? All of it, Ben! All of it. Mine. I’m peaking Ben. It’s my time now. Our time.

Ben: this is some pitch, all this. You must need me pretty bad. What do you want?

Emperor: I want you to take over the galaxy. You... and your knights of Ren.

Ben: is that it?

Emperor: no... I want you to end it... Your blood is the key to a new future. You’re going to sit at the throne of all the galaxies, my boy. You’re going to set this whole thing free.

Ben: in the prophecy, you lose. We’re destined to lose sheev.

Emperor: I have been every voice. 
Snoke: you have ever heard. 
Vader: inside your head.

Emperor: I’m no puppeteer Ben. I don’t make things happen. It doesn’t work like that.

Ben: what did you do to me?

Emperor: free will. It’s like butterfly wings. Once touched they never get off the ground. I only set the stage. You pull your own strings. 

Ben: what did you do to me? 

Emperor: a lightsaber? In here? 

Ben: DAMM IT!!! WHAT DID YOU DO TO ME?!!!!

Emperor: well... on a scale of 1-10... 10 being the most evil act of destroying the Jedi order and 1 being your average slaughtering a village of sand people. I’d say, not to be cruel... you and I got it on about a 7.

Ben: FUCK YOU!!!! (Slashes the emperor)

Emperor: Got me!!!! Got me!!!! Yes!!!!! Step it up son!!!! Come on!!!!! That’s good!!!! You got to hold on to the fury! That’s the last thing to go! That’s the final hiding place. It’s the final fig leaf.

Ben: who are you?

Emperor: who am I? Who are you? Supreme leader of the first order. Leader of the knights of Ren. Why? Why do you think? Because you’re so fucking good. Yes. But why? 

Ben: because you’re my grandfathers creator?

Emperor: I’m a little more than that Ben, awfully hot in that throne room, wasn’t it? What’s the mission, Ben? To finish what you started, Ben. Time to let old things die. 

Ben: what are you?

Emperor: I have so many names.

Ben: sidious?

Emperor: call me great grandfather.

Ben: skywalker, luke, he knew it. He knew it. He knew it, so you destroyed him and the Jedi order. 

Emperor: you’re blaming me for skywalker? I hope you’re kidding. Luke you could have saved him and the Jedi order anytime you wanted. All he wanted was a good student. You wanted power. 

Ben: that’s a lie. 

Emperor: face it you wanted to be powerful ever since you learned your heritage. 

Ben: that’s not true. You don’t know what we had. 

Emperor: I’m on your side.

Ben: you’re a liar! (Goes to leave)

Emperor: there’s nothing out there for you. Don’t be a paln of the Jedi. Stop deluding yourself. Skywalker told you to control your feelings. What did he say? “Reach out with your feelings” didn’t he say that? What did you do? “I will destroy you, and her, and all of it” remember? 

Ben: I know what you did. You set me up!

Emperor: who told you to become this evil great creation? Who made that choice?

Ben: it’s entrapment. You set me up!

Emperor: and Han? The direction you took! Hutts, slavers, federation, all feeding at the same trough. Who’s ideas were those? 

Ben: you played me!

Emperor: it was a test! Your test! And Rey, knowing she could possibly turn. Seeing her power! What did you do? You offered to train her! 

Ben: you brought me in. You put me there! You made her powerful!

Emperor: I don’t do that, Ben! The day you spoke to the helmet what did I say to you? What were my words to you? The call to the light, you didn’t want it.

Ben: Light!!!!! I don’t follow the light!!!! I’m powerful!!!! I’m powerful!!!!! I’m a supreme leader!!!!! That’s my job that’s what I do!!!!!

Emperor: I rest my case. Skywalker Blood... definitely my favorite influence. Ben it’s so basic. Self-love. The unlimited power. It’s not that you didn’t care for skywalker, Ben... it’s just that you were a little more involved with someone else. Yourself.

Ben: you’re right. I did it all. I betrayed him. I let the light side go. 

Emperor: don’t be too hard on yourself, Ben. You wanted something more. Believe me. I left plagius behind and just kept going. You can’t keep punishing yourself. It’s awesome how far you’ve come. I didn’t make it easy. Couldn’t. Not for you. I’ve had so many apprentices. I’ve had so many disappointments. Mistake after mistake. Then there’s you. 

Ben: what do you want from me? 

Emperor: I want you to be yourself. You know, I tell you boy... guilt... it’s like a bag of fucking bricks. All you got to do... is set it down. Ik what you’re going through. I’ve been there. Let it go.

Ben: I can’t do that. 

Emperor: who you carrying all those bricks for? Skywalker? I tell you... let me give you a little inside information about Skywalker. Skywalker likes to watch. He’s a prankster. Think about it. It’s the goof of all time. Feel, but don’t think. Reach out, but don’t take. And while you’re jumping from one foot to the other what is he doing? He’s laughing his sick fucking ass off! He’s a tightass! He’s a failure! He’s a supposed keeper of the peace! Follow that? Never! 

Ben: better to reign in the dark then serve the light. Is that it?
